{"tid":2032193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾志豪： 64晚會唔係維園搞，頭條唔係港台播 意義差好遠亦會失去其影響力","createTime":"2020-05-24T02:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T02:47:39.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c9ec51725dc13eb39d9861a1fa2ac499cda071","tid":2032193,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"「維園燭光的意義在於官式，經過申請，政府批准，讓你在此搞集會，跟民間自己搞不同。同一道理《頭條》最重要核心價值是在官方公營電台，用公帑在主流媒體講官方不喜歡聽的說話。上網做？鬼唔知咩，但意義差好遠。」<br />\n<br />\n肉中刺，離開皮肉，便是一條痛不了的刺，魏京生、王丹、陳光誠等異見人士離開中國便失去影響力，怪不得有建制派議員建議《頭條》轉戰網上，曾志豪說：「是同一思維，他不是要你姓曾和姓吳的消失於世界，只要不讓我看見你們在官台就OK。」<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200524/6XHMP6VD6XQRSAV47B3Y7WAMS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200524%2F6XHMP6VD6XQRSAV47B3Y7WAMS4%2F&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=ed0aac07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200524%2F6XHMP6VD6XQRSAV47B3Y7WAMS4%2F&h=c21b333f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200524/6XHMP6VD6XQRSAV47B3Y7WAMS4/</a>"},{"pid":"22b128881213be4bf5f6a01fb73757d511752606","tid":2032193,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"形式 意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b4418f2e128c94b0c84b471e90c19a3e86053d","tid":2032193,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22b128881213be4bf5f6a01fb73757d511752606","tid":2032193,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"形式 意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"主要係 唔係官方批准 搞咩都無肯定性"},{"pid":"8bd9aeb09472d7379d1cd497523739c796bf3ebd","tid":2032193,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3b4418f2e128c94b0c84b471e90c19a3